We sell Canadian made solid wood furniture-everything from live edge tables, sideboards, end tables, buffets, coffee tables, chairs, bunk beds, desks, bookcases, beds, night tables, toy boxes, curios, pantries, stools, armoires, chests, bars, mirrors, benches, storage units, deacons benches, huntboards. entry tables, change tables, children's tables and chairs and cribs. services: Take home our unpainted furniture and finish it yourself or have our professional finishers do the work for you. We also work with movie and TV production companies to supply furniture for their movies and TV shows.

profile:
The focus of Wood On Wood is to promote our designs and build beautiful long lasting furniture. We work directly with the home owners, their designers, architects, and home builders  to transform  their designs into products with excellent quality and all the features they imagined.  The factory works closely with the clients. Since 1995 until today there has not been a project that we were not able to deliver to perfection. Our head designer Carla Goncalves works directly in the factory to ensure that all products are made 100% according to the original designs, and to ensure the highest quality.

I personally have been involved in the world of furniture for as long as i can recall and  when leaving university in 1995 decided that i was following my passion  of making awesome projects in the furniture industry.

1995 is the year that both Carla and I decided to make Contemporary Furniture in Solid Wood and Custom Made. This was the cornerstone of our work. The result was amazing, and what we have learned from clients since then shows in  each piece of furniture that we build.

We use the best and Eco-friendly products, and base our production on the skills of artisans and woodworkers, every piece is handmade to order.
name: Wood On Wood
